{"tid":531461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第四次工業革命會唔會係3d打印技術既成熟同普及？","createTime":"2018-01-17T00:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T16:05:27.000Z","uid":24615,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d684d7f2dec8498d67f10e15e43b79a68a5d7815","tid":531461,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:24:06.000Z","msg":"一但3d打印技術成熟同普及（技術成熟到可以用佢黎/幫手生產到複雜物料既野，例如一個摩打）<br />\n家家戶戶都可以自己整生活必需品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三產業亦唔需要向第二產業買咁多現成貨品<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大量工廠會消失，大量第三產業都會消失<br />\n得番高精密度既生產業，原料複雜既生產業例如藥廠<br />\n<br />\n社會會變番工業革命前既手工業社會<br />\n家家戶戶自己生產，小資都係自己生產d貨品<br />\n「品牌」已經唔會再存在<br />\n集中生產已經冇任何價值，所以大部分工廠會消失<br />\n資本主義既根基都會受動搖"},{"pid":"9e08f5668cbd8ed6fa143a12a52b57850010ec53","tid":531461,"uid":3063,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:34:37.000Z","msg":"商店唔賣商品<br />\n賣設計圖"},{"pid":"da82d51178cd0f581d493f1adf86f6b73dab31af","tid":531461,"uid":163916,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"首先，摩打一定印唔到，你點印油漆包線，磁石電工鋼同Ball bearing?<br />\n<br />\nP.S.磁石要充磁，做電工鋼唔係簡單過程。<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印唔到電子野。<br />\n印到高精度金屬的機賣緊過千萬。<br />\nAuto-Cad軟體唔係人人識。"},{"pid":"9cb75dd89bd2060aa8cdecd4f41db22cb326a095","tid":531461,"uid":4493,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:47:10.000Z","msg":"Adidas已經試緊喺各地唔同門市即刻打印波鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣可以節省運輸同埋儲存成本<br />\n<br />\n鞋面用電腦編織 鞋底用打印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b9a4db17409bcc0de8feb6fa566791e1ddd79d","tid":531461,"uid":86960,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"da82d51178cd0f581d493f1adf86f6b73dab31af","tid":531461,"uid":163916,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"首先，摩打一定印唔到，你點印油漆包線，磁石電工鋼同Ball bearing?<br />\n<br />\nP.S.磁石要充磁，做電工鋼唔係簡單過程。<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印唔到電子野。<br />\n印到高精度金屬的機賣緊過千萬。<br />\nAuto-Cad軟體唔係人人識。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:48:48.000Z","msg":"Autocad 好多人識了 <br />\n但3D 果啲software 應該少人識啲"},{"pid":"6414842a0c10cdd0e825cbe408c3a543be8785cf","tid":531461,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:57:22.000Z","msg":"點解唔係ai+3d打印<br />\n直頭人都唔使<br />\n放部ai同個打印機係舖頭，信用卡俾錢<br />\n大把人失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a7be81afead8e7f99a50b70aed679b795595df","tid":531461,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:05:54.000Z","msg":"鋪頭放部3D打印機<br />\n預先儲存好晒所有產品打印程序<br />\n顧客去到就選要打印D咩, 俾錢, 打印, 拎走<br />\n成個retail過程變左唔洗員工<br />\n<br />\n鋪頭只要定時補足打印材料同維修部打印機<br />\n<br />\n新產品唔洗上架, online 更新打印機入便的設計圖就得"},{"pid":"8c3dbd318e31df70cf59b5b5711989969f75e61c","tid":531461,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:10:02.000Z","msg":"仲鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲d幾個人夾錢買部3d打印機番黎<br />\nprint乜都得<br />\n<br />\n到時係得設計同原材料值錢"},{"pid":"df07489183de688d0ab197f1ed290e07ef47bae0","tid":531461,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c3dbd318e31df70cf59b5b5711989969f75e61c","tid":531461,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:10:02.000Z","msg":"仲鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲d幾個人夾錢買部3d打印機番黎<br />\nprint乜都得<br />\n<br />\n到時係得設計同原材料值錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:11:53.000Z","msg":"到時海關 捉網上發佈3D程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n變左商業罪案調查秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed169f9761967491ca9ae2b91d667abe01aaf7b","tid":531461,"uid":48081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"89b9a4db17409bcc0de8feb6fa5