 />\nAuto-Cad軟體唔係人人識。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:48:48.000Z","msg":"Autocad 好多人識了 <br />\n但3D 果啲software 應該少人識啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:55:50.000Z","msg":"Autocad 要叫做普及先叫多人識<br />\n唔係話你讀engineering 嗰啲就叫識<br />\n再者個software 操作要容易同簡單<br />\n唔使打command 先至可以普及化"},{"pid":"491c00710cc7c3f16bce777363c7820c81e9f416","tid":531461,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:56:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>首先，摩打一定印唔到，你點印油漆包線，磁石電工鋼同Ball bearing?<br />\n<br />\nP.S.磁石要充磁，做電工鋼唔係簡單過程。<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印唔到電子野。<br />\n印到高精度金屬的機賣緊過千萬。<br />\nAuto-Cad軟體唔係人人識。</blockquote>Autocad 好多人識了 <br />\n但3D 果啲software 應該少人識啲</blockquote>Autocad 要叫做普及先叫多人識<br />\n唔係話你讀engineering 嗰啲就叫多人識<br />\n再者個software 操作要容易同簡單<br />\n唔使打command 先至可以普及化</blockquote>"},{"pid":"04bfe5b2db734dbac3fff577f9348965a509191f","tid":531461,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ed169f9761967491ca9ae2b91d667abe01aaf7b","tid":531461,"uid":48081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"89b9a4db17409bcc0de8feb6fa566791e1ddd79d","tid":531461,"uid":86960,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"da82d51178cd0f581d493f1adf86f6b73dab31af","tid":531461,"uid":163916,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"首先，摩打一定印唔到，你點印油漆包線，磁石電工鋼同Ball bearing?<br />\n<br />\nP.S.磁石要充磁，做電工鋼唔係簡單過程。<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印唔到電子野。<br />\n印到高精度金屬的機賣緊過千萬。<br />\nAuto-Cad軟體唔係人人識。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T00:48:48.000Z","msg":"Autocad 好多人識了 <br />\n但3D 果啲software 應該少人識啲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:16:07.000Z","msg":"仲autocad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過撚哂時啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"咁邊隻3D CAD入時?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59db7b83a367837195efcf77abe135c253c06cea","tid":531461,"uid":4493,"